cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.IR 

The paper deals with credit card fraud detection using active learning strategies, which involves machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with security and privacy issues related to credit card fraud, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves the use of data analysis techniques, which falls under the category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper involves the use of information retrieval techniques to query unlabeled transactions, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
